title: China’s Comac on Track to Miss C919 Delivery Target by Half
description: Commercial Aircraft Corp of China Ltd. is set to miss a revised delivery target for its marquee C919 single-aisle jet, dealing a blow to its global ambitions after trade war-induced headwinds helped hamper production.
